31
00:04:05.520 --> 00:04:06.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Eres increíble.

32
00:04:08.480 --> 00:04:09.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
